Package: panoramic
Title: PANORAMIC: Meta-Analysis of Spatial Colocalization in Spatial Omics
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jacob", "Chang", email = "jachang4@stanford.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment=c(ORCID="0000-0002-3719-7949"))
Description: PANORAMIC provides a pipeline for quantifying and meta-analyzing
    spatial colocalization between cell types in spatial omics experiments.
    The package prepares SpatialExperiment inputs, computes Loh-bootstrap
    spatial summary functions (e.g. L- and K-functions) for cell-type pairs
    across samples, and performs random-effects meta-analysis to assess
    group-level differences in spatial colocalization.
URL: https://github.com/plevritis-lab/panoramic
BugReports: https://github.com/plevritis-lab/panoramic/issues    
